trans-unit.target: 一个哈希破解的网络服务

trans-unit.source: Jabbercracky is a hash-cracking web service which provides a two-phase cracking solution. First, it will attempt to crack a hash using rainbow tables, if available. If that fails, it will resort to using GPU-accelerated brute forcing. Jabbercracky supports MD5, LM, NTLM, and more! nn
trans-unit.target: Jabbercracky是一个哈希破解的网络服务,它提供了一个两阶段的破解方案。首先,它将尝试使用彩虹表(如果有的话)来破解哈希。如果失败了,它将使用GPU加速的蛮力破解。Jabbercracky支持MD5、LM、NTLM等!nn。
